<doc id="1107743" wikidata="Q1772780" url="?curid=1107743" title="Mailx">
<text>mailx is a Unix utility program for sending and receiving mail, also known as a Mail User Agent program. Being a console application with a command syntax similar to ed, it is the POSIX standardized variant of the Berkeley Mail utility.

