<doc id="1107777" wikidata="Q700778" url="?curid=1107777" title="Arrondissement of Béthune">
<text>The arrondissement of Béthune is an arrondissement of France in the Pas-de-Calais department in the Hauts-de-France region. It has 104 communes. Its population is 292,114 (2021), and its area is .

==Composition==

